        "id": 1001621
      },
      "writtenOn": "2026-04-22T19:20:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We have code that supports other fan types paths than just fan_tach, it seems problematic to assume this path.[1]\n\n[1] https://github.com/openbmc/bmcweb/blob/bff66f9b658822be3fec688d56efbcef572922c5/redfish-core/include/utils/sensor_utils.hpp#L224",
      "range": {
