      "writtenOn": "2026-04-23T19:42:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good points. The plan for the next patchset is to drop the name-match entirely and use the sensors/inventory association via getAssociatedSubTree. For multi-rotor fans it would walk every tach returned, and any Functional\u003dfalse flips Health to Critical.",
